data.description: 4 bedrooms 3 bathroom home for sale in North Andrews, tile floors through out the house, remodeled bathroom and kitchen about 5 years ago, hurricane shutters for every window and doors, garage converted into a room, roof only five years old, covered patio and fenced back yard, recessed lights in living areas, newer sliding doors to go to the patio, living rooms are freshly painted, open front porch, excellent location, close to restaurants, gym and shopping.
